    <h3 {...{
      "id": "books-categories-and-book-ratings"
    }}>{`Books, Categories, and Book Ratings`}</h3>
    <p>{`This lesson will start by fleshing out the Book, Category, and BookRating models with their respective Spring Repositories.`}</p>
